Usurper Reborn v0.60.8 [BETA]
A modern remake of the 1993 BBS classic.
*kicking fantasy* Gangs, politics, romance.
Fight monsters or murder other players. Become
king, marry, have children, found a dynasty.
Descend 100 dungeon floors. Defeat the seven
Old Gods. Ascend to godhood yourself.
BBS door, standalone, online multiplayer.
GPL v2 - Free and open source.
https://usurper-reborn.net
